RED_0:"It tastes bad, I shouldn't have eaten it…",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CRED_1:"D'oh, now my tummy is feeling queasy!",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CRED_2:"These berries are not for eating…",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_CVIOLET:"Saffron",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_CVIOLET:"Beautiful flowers that are used for flavoring in faraway countries.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CVIOLET_0:"I think it's used as a spice, but I'm not sure…",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CVIOLET_1:"I should probably experiment with it. What if I make something useful?",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_CWHITE:"Daisy",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_CWHITE:"It's not just a beautiful flower, but also a useful medicinal herb!",TEXT_NARRATOR_USE_ITEM_CWHITE_0:"Slavya makes some chamomile tea.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CWHITE_1:"It smells great!",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CWHITE_2:"A simple but beautiful flower, widely used in medicine.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_CYELLOW:"Tansy",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_CYELLOW:"It looks like a chamomile with no petals.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CYELLOW_0:"It tastes like grass.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CYELLOW_1:"Why am I eating this?",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CYELLOW_2:"I'd rather use this in a potion.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_CORANGE:"Globeflower",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_CORANGE:"Beautiful flowers that can be a great decoration.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CORANGE_0:"These flowers are really beautiful. They could be used in a bouquet and make a nice decoration.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_CBLACK:"Henbane",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_CBLACK:"Poisonous flowers petals.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CBLACK_0:"These flowers' petals look suspicious… I think they are poisonous.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_SPONGE:"Sponge",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_SPONGE:"It's soft and it holds water really well, it can even deal with the most stubborn stains.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_SPONGE_0:"An imported sponge. It's soft and it holds water really well, it can even deal with the most stubborn stains.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_APPLE:"Apple",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_APPLE:"Fresh apples — the best food for a young potion maker.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_APPLE_0:"Apples are the greatest food ever.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_APPLE_1:"I think, in my previous life, I ate only them…",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_APPLE_2:"But I shouldn't eat too many, or else I will get a tummy ache.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_BLIN:"Pancakes",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_BLIN:"Fine soft pancakes. It's a great snack.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_BLIN_0:"Tastes brilliant! I could add some filling to them next time.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_PANCAKES:"Thick pancakes",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_PANCAKES:"Puffy thick pancakes.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_PANCAKES_0:"Pans and cakes!",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_PANCAKES_1:"I shouldn't eat too many, I might gain weight. But it's important to indulge sometimes!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_OMELETTE:"Omelet",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_OMELETTE:"Hot omelet with scallions.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_OMELETTE_0:"Puffy omelet — a great choice!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_YAY:"Fried eggs",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_YAY:"Simple, tasty and hearty meal.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_YAY_0:"Fried eggs — easy and very fulfilling!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_PIROZHKI:"Apple pasties",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_PIROZHKI:"Pasties with apple filling, baked to golden brown.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_PIROZHKI_0:"Apple pasties! I love them!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_DOUGH:"Dough",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_DOUGH:"Rich dough for baking. It will work just fine for pasties and for pancakes.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_DOUGH_0:"I should cook it and create something tasty!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_EGGMILK:"Beaten eggs",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_EGGMILK:"Whisk milk and eggs together.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_EGGMILK_0:"I should cook it and create something tasty!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_EGGFLOUR:"Batter",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_EGGFLOUR:"Flour and eggs.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_EGGFLOUR_0:"I should cook it and create something tasty!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_FLOURMILK:"Pre-dough",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_FLOURMILK:"Milk and flour mixture. Doesn't look very edible.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_FLOURMILK_0:"I should cook it and create something tasty!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_CIDER:"Cider",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_CIDER:"Sparkling beverage made from fermented apples.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_CIDER_0:"Pepper-upper! It's very invigorating!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_PAN:"Frying pan",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_PAN:"A cast iron frying pan with a wooden handle. I can make a lot of tasty things with it.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_PAN_0:"A cast iron frying pan is a great weapon, by the way!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_DIRTY_PAN:"Dirty pan",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_DIRTY_PAN:"A cast iron pan with burnt on leftover food.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_DIRTY_PAN_0:"It's so dirty. What can I wash it with…?",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_DIRTY_PAN_0:"What do we have here? Hm, it's quite heavy. Looks like some ancient utensil.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_DIRTY_PAN_1:"I wonder if I can use it… either way, it's a good heavy weapon.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_DIRTY_PAN_2:"Wow! A frying pan! Great! Now I just need to wash it — and I can use it for cooking.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_DIRTY_PAN_3:"Wow! Another frying-pan.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_DIRTY_PAN_4:"I wonder how many of them I can find here. I suppose I could this one.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_FLOUR:"Flour",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_FLOUR:"Fluffy wheat flour, perfect for baking.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_FLOUR_0:"Concentrated carbohydrates. I wouldn't eat pure flour even during a famine!",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_FLOUR_0:"Wow! You can find absolutely everything here — even flour.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_FLOUR_1:"When you have flour, you can always bake something tasty…",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_FLOUR_2:"Even if you don’t eat it, you can always sell it.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_FLOUR_3:"Hmm… Flour again. Ok, maybe I’ll bake something.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_FLOUR_4:"Wow, more flour! Looks like I can bake even more things!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_EGGS:"Eggs",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_EGGS:"Fresh chicken eggs. I can cook something tasty with them.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_EGGS_0:"I could fry them…",TEXT_NARRATOR_USE_ITEM_EGGS_1:"Slavya accidentally drops an egg.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_EGGS_2:"My, my! I'm so clumsy!",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_EGGS_3:"What a waste of food and I have to clean up this mess, to top it off.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_EGGS_0:"Whenever I forget to close the door, my neighbor's hens wonder inside. Fortunately for me, they will sometimes lay some eggs. Which comes in handy for cooking.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_EGGS_1:"I wonder if my neighbor left some eggs for me or is it just a hen hiding from the heat…",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_EGGS_2:"Yay, more eggs! Great, I can cook with them or sell them.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_MILK:"milk",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_MILK:"Fresh milk. I can cook something with it.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_MILK_0:"I don't really like drinking milk. I'd rather use it for cooking.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_MILK_0:"Milk… It’s from my neighbor, Auntie Masha. She gives me a jug of milk from time to time. She leaves it in the barn to keep it fresh and cool.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_MILK_1:"I’m actually not a milk fan but maybe I can cook something nice with it.",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_MILK_2:"Auntie Masha visited again! Now I have some milk for cooking. What should I make…",TEXT_SL_PICK_ITEM_MILK_3:"It seems the milk yield was especially good today.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_POT4_TENTACLE:"Potion of Sea Monster",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_POT4_TENTACLE:"A weird creature in a jar.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_TENTACLE_0:"And how should I use it?",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_TENTACLE_1:"Let's keep it in the jar.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_TENTACLE_2:"I'll sell it, maybe somebody else would like it as a pet.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_POT4_NEKO:"Beasterin",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_POT4_NEKO:"It helps to wake up your inner beast.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_NEKO_0:"I don't want to turn into a cat again.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_NEKO_1:"Growing extra appendages is not a pleasant experience.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_POT4_SLEEP:"Potion of Heavy Sleeping",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_POT4_SLEEP:"A great insomnia remedy.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_SLEEP_0:"I don't want to go to sleep.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_SLEEP_1:"I will try it when I have insomnia.",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_POT4_INVISIBLE:"Potion of Invisibility",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_POT4_INVISIBLE:"The potion of thieves and lovers.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_INVISIBLE_0:"Enough, this potion is stupid!",TEXT_ITEM_NAME_POT4_FULLHEAL:"Potion of Absolute Healing",TEXT_ITEM_DESCR_POT4_FULLHEAL:"The most important potion for the healer.",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_FULLHEAL_0:"Wow, I feel completely reborn!",TEXT_SL_USE_ITEM_POT4_FULLHEAL_